dc_title_s: County and township map of Arizona and New Mexico / S. Augustus Mitchell.; Arizona and New Mexico
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. "Entered according to an Act of Congress in the year 1881 by S. Augustus Mitchell in the Office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington." Plate 92 from Mitchell's New General Atlas, Containing Maps Of The Various Countries Of The World, Plans Of Cities, Etc., Embraced In Ninety-Three Quarto Maps. 1 map : col. ; 35 x 55 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
